3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003255_500335236223788_5223893071272402515_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rcnRXA6b4R0Q7kNvgGgwLSk&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDs6syyC7HVb5PV3cmqaT6bXB6S_KOaD8-mi2Fb60K5ow&oe=672DDFA1"}, "display_name": "Caral civilization, the oldest in America", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Immersive experience \"Pututus Ceremonial Hall\". Immersive virtual reality experience - VR inspired by the values \u200b\u200band social history of the Caral Civilization, the oldest in America, of the \u00abPututus Ceremonial Hall\u00bb located on the top of the Main Public Building, upper part of \u00abPe\u00f1ico, City of Social Integration\u00bb, during the Early Formative 1 (1800-1500 BC). Pe\u00f1ico is one of the 25 urban centers identified in the Supe Valley, 30 years ago, by the team of professionals led by the Peruvian archaeologist Dr. Ruth Shady, principal researcher of Caral.\nThe team of specialists of the Caral Archaeological Zone makes available this immersive virtual reality experience - VR in which all cybernauts will be able to approach the main values \u200b\u200bof the Caral Civilization.", "short_description": "Immersive virtual reality (VR) experience that allows you to explore the \u00abCeremonial Hall of the Pututus\u00bb of the Caral Civilization, the oldest in America, highlighting its values \u200b\u200band social history. Developed by specialists from the Caral Archaeological Zone, this experience offers a virtual tour of Pe\u00f1ico, one of the urban centers of the Supe Valley, investigated by the team of professionals led by Peruvian archaeologist Dr. Ruth Shady, principal investigator of Caral."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.zonacaral.gob.pe/museo/PolItica_de_privacidad.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Zona Arqueologica Caral", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.gob.pe/caral", "categ